,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"估人地點估價其實更緊要，你同大市睇法唔align都GG啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:23:38.000Z","msg":"點解要同大市睇法一致？"},{"pid":"19604ddff7be4def8c4082608cce297f08a30a96","tid":1698927,"uid":218716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"建議連仔去business valuation firm 做下了解DCF 的奧秘。用你對Discount rate 的認識，知道d analyst apply 緊什麼discount rate. 再進而知道overvalue 定undervalue.<br />\n<br />\n當然economic moat 係好重要，有wide moat 的discount rate 低d, 估值高d. Narrow moat 的discount rate 高d, 估值低d.  No moat 當然最差。<br />\n<br />\n總之，了解DCF 對買股大有幫助"},{"pid":"cfd93e2a7584ffd1e6b27eeb837a999fc56ec89b","tid":1698927,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4842fcf1587780830e47c2c1e9258279ac7e2d5e","tid":1698927,"uid":143694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"我會用ratio 去估多過用CAPM 呢類計<br />\n姐係用PE PS EV/EBITDA 呢類 搵番historical average 去估算<br />\nCAPM 入面太多assumption"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:34:58.000Z","msg":"行業估值法同每年頂底價 financial ratio 真係好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}